Ð¡ontent script for GitLab .../-/issues/boards page. Allows you quickly and conveniently work with large number of issues. 
Folded issue card displays all the necessary key information:
- milestone date;
- number of approvals;
- quantity of relevant merge requests;
- last relevant merge's pipeline status.
Unfolded card allows in one click:
- open last relevant MR's changes page;
- open milestone page;
- mark latest MR as draft/ready;
- merge last MR;
- approve or revoke approval.

Also there is integration with GitLab CD allows to open in new tab deployed branch. This function is usefull for testing frontend projects, just input backend URL on the extension's settings page. For the correct work of some functions, you have to input on the settings page your personal api token, which can be created in the GitLab profile settings.
